# 2️⃣ Strategy Pattern म्हणजे काय?

### 📘 Simple Definition

> **Strategy Pattern** म्हणजे
> “एका कामासाठी वेगवेगळे algorithms वेगळ्या classes मध्ये define करणे
> आणि runtime ला algorithm change करण्याची मुभा देणे.”

📌 Meaning:

* **What to do** → fixed
* **How to do** → changeable

---

# 3️⃣ Strategy Pattern चे 3 main parts

### 1️⃣ Strategy (Interface)

👉 Algorithm define करतो

### 2️⃣ Concrete Strategies

👉 Actual implementations

### 3️⃣ Context

👉 Strategy वापरणारा class

---

# 4️⃣ Simple Example (Teacher Flow)

## 🎯 Example: Payment System

---

## Step 1️⃣ Strategy Interface

```java
interface PaymentStrategy {
    void pay(int amount);
}
```

---

## Step 2️⃣ Concrete Strategies

### Cash Payment

```java
class CashPayment implements PaymentStrategy {

    @Override
    public void pay(int amount) {
        System.out.println("Paid " + amount + " using Cash");
    }
}
```

### Card Payment

```java
class CardPayment implements PaymentStrategy {

    @Override
    public void pay(int amount) {
        System.out.println("Paid " + amount + " using Card");
    }
}
```

### UPI Payment

```java
class UpiPayment implements PaymentStrategy {

    @Override
    public void pay(int amount) {
        System.out.println("Paid " + amount + " using UPI");
    }
}
```

---

## Step 3️⃣ Context Class

```java
class PaymentContext {

    private PaymentStrategy paymentStrategy;

    public PaymentContext(PaymentStrategy paymentStrategy) {
        this.paymentStrategy = paymentStrategy;
    }

    public void setPaymentStrategy(PaymentStrategy paymentStrategy) {
        this.paymentStrategy = paymentStrategy;
    }

    public void payAmount(int amount) {
        paymentStrategy.pay(amount);
    }
}
```

👉 Context ला **algorithm कसा आहे हे माहित नाही**
तो फक्त `pay()` call करतो.

---

## Step 4️⃣ Client Code

```java
public class StrategyDemo {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        PaymentContext context = new PaymentContext(new CashPayment());
        context.payAmount(100);

        // runtime strategy change
        context.setPaymentStrategy(new CardPayment());
        context.payAmount(200);

        context.setPaymentStrategy(new UpiPayment());
        context.payAmount(300);
    }
}
```

---

## 5️⃣ Output समजून घ्या

```
Paid 100 using Cash
Paid 200 using Card
Paid 300 using UPI
```

👉 Same Context
👉 Different behaviour
👉 Runtime change ✔

