# 6️⃣ Strategy Pattern vs if-else (Important)

| Aspect      | if-else  | Strategy  |
| ----------- | -------- | --------- |
| Readability | Poor     | Clean     |
| Extensible  | ❌ No     | ✅ Yes     |
| OCP         | ❌ Breaks | ✅ Follows |
| Testing     | Hard     | Easy      |

