# 8️⃣ Strategy Pattern + Java 8 (Bonus)

Using **Lambda**

```java
PaymentStrategy cash = amount ->
        System.out.println("Paid " + amount + " using Cash");

PaymentContext context = new PaymentContext(cash);
context.payAmount(500);
```

