# 9️⃣ Common Mistakes (Interview Trap)

❌ Strategy inside `if-else`
❌ Too many responsibilities in Context
❌ Strategy with state (be careful)

---

# 🔟 Interview-Ready Answer

> **Strategy Pattern defines a family of algorithms, encapsulates each one, and makes them interchangeable at runtime.
> It eliminates conditional logic and promotes open-closed principle by allowing new strategies without modifying existing code.**

---

## 🧠 Golden Line (Remember This)

> **Strategy lets behaviour change without changing the class.**

